    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though the engine has a minor oil seep and the brakes will likely need service within the next 5,000 miles. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections.",
      "price": 19500.0,
